Rt Hon Francis Ogbonnaya Nwifuru has been re-elected Speaker of the Ebonyi State House of Assembly. Nwifuru, who presided over the fifth House of Assembly was re-elected moments ago by members of the sixth Assembly after its proclamation by Governor David Umahi. He was re-elected by the people of Izzi West state constituency for a third term in the April 9th Governorship and State Assembly election. Details shortlyâ€¦